description.displayText: Caroline served as a nanny for me off and on for several years.  She has stayed in my home and cared for my two children, my pets, and maintained the household during my business travels.  She followed my directions flawlessly and demonstrated true reliability.  Caroline's vibrant personality is magnetic to both, children and adults.

description.displayText: Caroline has done a wonderful job babysitting our 2year old daughter. I'm not one to leave my baby with just anyone and I feel very comfortable leaving her with Caroline. My daughter is very comfortable with her and we are impressed with her experience and knowledge of early childhood. I highly recommend Caroline for any nanny or babysitting position. She is excellent with children...and dogs too.

description.displayText: Caroline has babysat for my two kids (ages 17 months and 5) and they both love her! She's great with kids and a reliable, fun, babysitter. She's babysat for us both during the day and for date nights on the weekend. Would definitely recommend her.
